Welcome!

This is a new MagicGrid project for model based system specification, logical architecture, and design. Use the predefined structure of packages to skip organizing the model.


You can make this view the index diagram by adding references to specific views (diagrams, tables) into the framework representation.

 

Before creating your own MagicGrid project, you can study the built-in samples. They can be found in <installation directory>\samples\MagicGrid.
